channel.title: Need help 525, easy fix
channel.description:
Ok I just downloaded toksick525, and I clicked run, I got
Final-PvP The system cannot find the path specified. Press any key to continue...
I can run a 317, but whenever I do a 508 or 525 I can't O_o.
Here is the runserver.bat code.
[code]@echo off title Final-Pvp 24/7 Echo Final-Pvp cd ../build "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\java.exe" net/com/codeusa/Server 43594 pause[/code]
